# Naemon VimCrypt Vault Broker

## v1.5.1 (2026-03-20)

- Rebuild for current Naemon broker API (packaging/version bump only).

## v1.5.0 (2026-02-06)

- Rebuild for current Naemon broker API (packaging/version bump only).

## v1.4.4 (2025-06-03)

- Rebuild for current Naemon broker API (packaging/version bump only).

## v1.4.3 (2025-02-19)

- Add security warning about passing vault macros as parameters (values can leak via `ps`).

## v1.4.2 (2024-01-04)

- Replace `naemon.org` references with `naemon.io`.

## v1.4.0 (2022-11-11)

- Packaging/version bump only.

## v1.3.1 (2022-04-28)

- Add systemd documentation for providing the master password.
- Clear the master password environment variable again after startup.
- Fix default filename in example configuration.

## v1.3.0 (2021-11-05)

- Add packaging (Debian/RPM spec files) and build requirements.
- Rename module filename to `naemon_vimvault` and clean up build system.
- Add support for reading the master password from `NAEMON_VIM_MASTER_PASSWORD`.
- Support non-numeric vault macro names.
- Fail fast if no macros were found; improve logging and general cleanup.

## v0.0.1 (2021-06-18)

- Initial release.
